 style=\"color: red;\">毓民如果自己不參選，改為支持港獨派參選，就變成為過去陷害制憲救港聯盟的一群賣港賊抬轎</span>，他個人不能取得立法會議席，還會自滅政治道德，可以埋單收檔。在公在私，我是極之不願意見到毓民這位政壇元老幫壞人抬轎，斷送香港政壇道德與他個人的名譽的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾撚毒 .. </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然大前提是毓民老哥不要用港獨議程來參與選舉，免得被選舉辦事處取消參選資格及加強人大釋法的惡劣效應。這方面要請他老哥變通一下、忍耐一下。<br />\n<br />\n順勢屈毓民支持港獨<br />\n人地毓民一直講明唔支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04da92a922a88fb8d2c0dc8994a73b292c0bb85","tid":247823,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"陣間cap圖又話我哋係青政啲人喺度挑撥離間"},{"pid":"e60a39b73d03405a253e7801de5e4f6f473dca54","tid":247823,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/173707_cbe9fff5c14abf19991e228586c9e691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F173707_cbe9fff5c14abf19991e228586c9e691.jpg&h=1d8bf6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傑出熱狗系列<br />\n一句KO晒大家"},{"pid":"299f250c196fe1eb1cd75be73c0e23a3c482cd6a","tid":247823,"uid":53016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: violet;\">雲伯表示 : 『咩碌撚當你臭四炸行撚開啦，本大爺收左order一定要搞死青政無得出黎選』</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲伯對於成立 反黃復仇者聯盟2.0 表示讚好<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/JwdZ1U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FJwdZ1U.jpg&h=f4a0ce63&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明讚咁踩係呢隻老狐狸一直既風格<br />\n<br />\n佢o岩o岩先同毓民眼中釘癌鳳凰果堆畜牲談笑風生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f737955900f7e094bae11801383a41fd9ba52b53","tid":247823,"uid":34838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"睇陳雲嘅文字同見佢刻意塑造多個性格<